{
  "id": "RAW_fcc60ebb",
  "title": "Claude Code 狂暴更新周！一周发 5 个版本，数十个新功能！好用！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500329&idx=1&sn=751cb5cf7451de9b07f90a23f41dcab4",
  "date": "2026-01-11 18:27:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #faf9f7 !important;padding: 20px 24px 56px 24px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。Claude Code从本周开始，就像疯了一样，一周内发布了5个版本！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从1月7日发布v2.1.0，到昨天的v2.1.4，不到一周，发布五个正式版本，共有一百多个项改动！</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;资深用户狂喜。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">不得不说，虽然Anthropic这家公司的CEO人品和格局不怎么样，但是他家的产品能力可真是牛。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">我列举几个感知比较强的功能，大家赶快去试试吧。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、语言设置</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">再也不需要输入“请使用中文回答了”你可以输入 /Config 找到语言设置</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29850746268656714\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"938\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016669\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=241353ad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBQpsA4vAmbWJGCU2P6ud8dq3MbE6dcnAxlAra9kIrrQ0ibkTRrEofd6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016671\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c51cd26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBymgUkIWKzvWhGR7LMVqg4w305XBjXTp4OymcSsfb0XsxX41TxLNW0Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">二、粘贴图片更加友好</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在粘贴多个图片后，可以用箭头按钮，选择不同的图片。如果把鼠标放上去，还会显示图片的路径。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2796296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016668\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3567134a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBiaCPicE28sdylN5RJVVCtgn0Giapeic23Llz5RnVkib5dKXmjSXiaQzLuS7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">对了，还修复了以前偶尔出现的 \"Image was too large\" 错误。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">三、Skill支持热重载</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是外网用户评价最好的功能。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前的痛点: 修改 skill 后必须重启整个会话</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在: ~/.claude/skills 或 .claude/skills 中的 skill 保存即生效</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">四、 Sub-agents 分叉上下文</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前的痛点： sub-agents太多，会污染上下文、会占用原本就宝贵的上下文窗口长度</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在：Skill 可以在独立的子代理中运行，不污染主上下文。五、Ctrl+B 统一后台运行</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在 Ctrl+B 可以</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时将所有正在运行的任务</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（包括所有bash命令、sub-agent等等）放到后台。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且，后台任务完成后显示干净的完成消息，不再是乱糟糟的原始输出。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">五、可以使用/plan命令触发计划模式</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前的痛点：需要按shift+tab切换到plan模式。这非常麻烦，尤其是我长期使用Bypass Permission Mode，不喜欢切换来切换去的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在任意位置打 /plan 即可在当次对话中使用计划模式</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，进入“对需求”阶段，而不用担心误操作代码。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以在使用bypass permission on的同时，用/plan来做计划了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.18055555555555555\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016670\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf877107&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBPuWJEYAhWqXmHzPicNu7XgIgShkH8aEjUzc7KM5Y84ibnicKkRuP6VIng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">六、云端和本地同步，会话传送</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">会话传送，这可真是太懂用户痛点了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们知道，其实Codex和Claude Code都有云端版本，但是以前被人诟病的是：云端和本地版本，很难协调。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">本次Claude Code解决了这个问题，允许用户在本地终端和 Web 界面之间无缝切换。还可以恢复和配置远程会话、与团队成员共享会话</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">只需要输入 /teleport 命令，就可以把当前会话传送到云端，使用云端资源继续执行。</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">七、通配符权限</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前: 每次运行命令都要点 Yes，权限疲劳</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在: 支持 * 通配符！</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">八、Shift+Enter 多行输入开箱即用</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前: 需要修改终端配置，非常麻烦。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在: iTerm2、WezTerm、Ghostty、Kitty 等终端直接支持</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">九、终端渲染bug修复</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code使用的多的朋友一定见过这个bug： 突然变成乱码。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7138888888888889\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016672\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=34d658c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBfVxribVG8gKyREgr1icJ3MUTic6ggreJMTTbVLfCcWllsHRyIWOICicOBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在这个Bug被修复了，还额外修复了中文、日文、韩文等语言的渲染和空行问题。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">十、Slash 命令自动补全增强</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前: / 必须在输入开头才能触发补全</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在: / 在输入的任何位置都能触发自动补全</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如图中的/commit 是我自定义的一个帮我审核代码、提交Git的Slash命令。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2009685230024213\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"826\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016673\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a381a08&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPB2K8z3TjZCgrozpq1EkuJYvEeia3icPia7FzBhGnfJVtLWHlSI7utUfgxA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">十一、性能和稳定性大幅提升</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">有明显体感，启动比以前快多了、使用起来也比以前快多了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">根据官方文档，实际上改进了很多小bug</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 32px 0;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">启动性能优化 - 多项优化加快启动速度</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">终端渲染性能提升 - 特别是 emoji、ANSI 码、Unicode 字符</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Jupyter Notebook 读取优化 - 多 cell 笔记本读取更快</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">内存泄漏修复 - git diff 解析时的内存问题</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">自动续写 - 响应被截断时自动继续，不再显示错误</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">压缩可靠性提升 - compaction 更稳定</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">十二、实时思考过程显示</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Claude Code思考过程中，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以使用 ctrl+o ，切换显示它的思考过程</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，以便于我们及时发现思考中的问题、及时干预。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2740740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016674\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fcb3b0c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBx9muFLr1Uzxg6l7R4VlmcZEzE6N9IwaRKuBVTamEu0Keo4FYfpsMBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5638888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016676\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2eda903d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPB8FAyX0eceVeEZicVGEHUkUibibKNqia7tqvWiadsnDHMZTddKtosEpvbLaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">十三、MCP 动态工具更新</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">引入了新功能: 支持 MCP list_changed 通知</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">MCP 服务器现在可以动态更新其可用的工具、prompts 和资源，无需重新连接！</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这对于工具配置频繁变化的工作流非常有用。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">十四、报错后自动继续</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前：有时候由于响应太长，会因 output token 限制被截断。比如，如果我们用Claude Code自动操作浏览器，遇到内容比较长的网页，就会遇到这个问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在：不会出问题了！</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code会在报错后自动继续，不展示错误信息，不会中断。</span></strong></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;color: #2b2b2b !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;margin: 48px 0 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;\"><span leaf=\"\">十五、所有Skill默认在菜单中可见</span></h3>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">似乎Claude Code这次是认真把Skill当成一等公民来对待了，所有在 /skills/ 目录下的skill，都会默认出现在菜单中，敲入斜杠就可以看看。如下图所示</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.16018518518518518\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016675\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1764fe01&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPB0ma7nmFcqcTYVv8Rv5icqz6SiaNeib2b1EiaEsOicLO3lotic1818mqXKIRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，这个功能好像是Codex先有的？如下图所示</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7333333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016677\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e642967&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBFjrjowJMrRmsVZegCuMaNBey1IKHC8niaia62NEvlagYUFVj1libaHj0Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 64px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.3), rgba(157, 200, 141, 0.3), transparent);\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">我是如何知道的这么多更新的？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">没那么难，查看官方文档就行。英文不好的朋友还可以借助Dia浏览器来理解。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><a href=\"https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6259259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100016678\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0455a694&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHts2gdvRUBP6kq6giaBUgPBbqxwzb5XcCphUZjwbDxH7ibpZrZu3D80YUT3FKpdNibSVz5S9QaXZDIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 64px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.3), rgba(157, 200, 141, 0.3), transparent);\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">赶快去试试吧，真的太好用了！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 32px 0 !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">我又要开始重度使用Claude Code了！</span></p